brief setup (wsl2 nvidia)

=== IGNORE FOR NOW ===
follow instructions: https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-downloads?target_os=Linux&target_arch=x86_64&Distribution=WSL-Ubuntu&target_version=2.0&target_type=deb_network
> wget https://developer.download.nvidia.com/compute/cuda/repos/wsl-ubuntu/x86_64/cuda-keyring_1.1-1_all.deb
> sudo dpkg -i cuda-keyring_1.1-1_all.deb
> sudo apt-get update
=== IGNORE FOR NOW ===

first time setup:
> sudo apt-get install build-essential libopencv-dev cmake nlohmann-json3-dev
> cmake -B build

build:
> cmake --build build